**Solution 1:**

Time complexity: `O(n)`
Space complexity: `O(1)`

```
class Solution 
{
    public int[] sortArrayByParityII(int[] A) 
    {
        int i = 0;
        int j = 1;

        while(i < A.length && j < A.length)
        {
            while(i < A.length && A[i] % 2 == 0) i += 2;
            while(j < A.length && A[j] % 2 == 1) j += 2;

            if(i < A.length && j < A.length)
                swap(A, i, j);
        }
        return A;
    }

    private void swap(int[] A, int i, int j)
    {
        int temp = A[i];
        A[i] = A[j];
        A[j] = temp;
    }
}
```

