explanation:
for every no. there are two possibilities: either its correct on its position or not correct.
also as there are equal no. of odd and even nos, so for every incorrect odd, there will be one incorrect even and vice-versa.

So we will just keep two pointers : one for odd positions and one for even positions.
Ignore those which are already at correct position.
Swap those which are at incorrect.

